snippet.title: Star Drift Evolution - Trailer
snippet.description:
Official Trailer of the upcoming minimalistic racing game Star Drift Evolution!
Wishlist it and download the free Demo from the official Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1005400/Star_Drift_Evolution/


Join the Discord server to interact with the devs and organize multiplayer games: https://discord.gg/gZqM6c9


Like the game on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Star-Drift-Evolution-107415277802537
